Class
Description

Generates customer arrival events based on an inter-arrival time distribution.

Singleton class representing the simulation clock.

Utility class for exporting simulation statistics to CSV format.

Represents a customer in the cafeteria simulation.

Abstract base class for discrete event simulation engines.

Represents an event in the discrete event simulation.

Manages the list of scheduled events in the simulation.

Enumeration of all event types in the simulation.

Enumeration of service point types in the cafeteria.

Utility class for trace/debug output with different severity levels.
